name: Experiment Or Die #123
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. The crypto space is VERY new. It's basically the wild west out here. If you are naive there is always a chance that someone will try and fleece you and you might have no idea what happened. Find your people. People you trust. Keep your head on a swivel, and beware of the wolf in sheep's clothing! Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
